{"tid":1558254,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[文宣行動］請支持星期三/四晚做全民文宣日","createTime":"2019-09-10T11:41:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T12:36:37.000Z","uid":64810,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5b6dcd778b8926e7293dcff5ddc1b30b8df24aee","tid":1558254,"uid":64810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T11:41:38.000Z","msg":"成撚日話冇文宣 因為個個做完都冇咩人貼<br />\n<br />\n有藍絲撕紙 又有藍絲打人 依家仲有蓋世太保同篤灰熱線呀<br />\n<br />\n日日10點嗌下 唱下歌係唔夠<br />\n<br />\n依家我地有大量違反人權既事可以做文宣呀<br />\n<br />\n文宣既水平已經大不如前 好簡單問你 知唔知今個星期六日要去邊 你都可能答唔到<br />\n<br />\n仆街！15號民陣遊行冇人講？？？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1557549\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1557549</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n所以一日要強化文宣方面 一黎可以反洗腦/宣傳之外 夠多人係連儂牆到都安全d <br />\n<br />\n我之前已經開過post問過  <br />\n動議 星期四晚做全民文宣日<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1543542\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1543542</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n星期三/四晚 9:00-10:00 可能係最好<br />\n唔太夜 又可以一齊嗌埋口號先走<br />\n<br />\n唔該 推下行動post啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32707b0529c02146390c70edb707429a943d918e","tid":1558254,"uid":64810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T11:42:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b8fa5a14de3ce710ee7ea214ad2c6af3ed7ae41","tid":1558254,"uid":64810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T11:43:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db2944cc8edbb246f9b785b14d56d781a805b51e","tid":1558254,"uid":64810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T11:44:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/face